"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-07-olympic-athlete-making-onlyfans-rowing-thanks-artistic-nudes-21377926\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"New Zealand's Robbie Manson may have finished sixth at the Olympic Games in the men's double skulls, but he has been making more money out of OnlyFans than rowing.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 11, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.8991600686927564, \"rank\": 0.09201601951659134, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 14, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Manson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Robbie Manson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Manson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Manson\"}, {\"begin\": 142, \"end\": 150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OnlyFans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"OnlyFans\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OnlyFans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OnlyFans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Manson, along with teammateJordanParry, reached the final inParisand managed sixth place, which is especially remarkable as Manson retired from rowing in 2020, returning in 2022.\", \"from\": 165, \"to\": 343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 165, \"end\": 171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marilyn_Manson\", \"score\": 0.9975648196587676, \"rank\": 0.0024411249205904596, \"text\": \"Manson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marilyn_Manson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marilyn_Manson\"}, {\"begin\": 289, \"end\": 295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marilyn_Manson\", \"score\": 0.9975648196587676, \"rank\": 0.0024411249205904596, \"text\": \"Manson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marilyn_Manson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marilyn_Manson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Away from the boat, the 34-year-old has been posing for OnlyFans content and he says he has been earning more through his racy photos than his races on water.\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 503, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 401, \"end\": 409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OnlyFans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"OnlyFans\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OnlyFans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OnlyFans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I get more than double what I would be on otherwise as an athlete - read into that what you will, but I am making more from OnlyFans than I am from rowing at this stage,' Manson toldReuters.\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 696, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 630, \"end\": 638, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OnlyFans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"OnlyFans\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OnlyFans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OnlyFans\"}, {\"begin\": 677, \"end\": 683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marilyn_Manson\", \"score\": 0.9975648196587676, \"rank\": 0.0024411249205904596, \"text\": \"Manson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marilyn_Manson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marilyn_Manson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I thought, if I am going to do it, you have to tell everyone, be really open and I think you need to feel that any publicity is good publicity.\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 842, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'The fact that I amgay, I have the gay following and the audience already, and I am slightly leaning into that.\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 955, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I would not say it's for everyone, (but) for other athletes, there is definitely an opportunity there.'\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 1059, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked what he generally posts on Only Fans, he said: 'Artistic nudes - I do not want to say too much more than that, I think people need to subscribe if they want to know what's exactly on there.\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1256, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'But in the captions, I just try to give people a little bit of an update from time to time, like what's going on in my life or training or journey to this point, towards theOlympics.'\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1442, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Manson posted an emotional message on social media after his Olympic exploits, thrilled with his return to elite rowing.\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1564, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1444, \"end\": 1450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marilyn_Manson\", \"score\": 0.9975648196587676, \"rank\": 0.0024411249205904596, \"text\": \"Manson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marilyn_Manson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marilyn_Manson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's hard to put into words what a journey this has been, but here goes,' he wrote onInstagram.\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1662, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Four years ago, I retired, never imagining I'd get back in a rowing boat.\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1737, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet here I am, not only back at the Olympics but in the A final!\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1802, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'While we are gutted that we could not clinch it today, I am incredibly proud that we made it to the top 6 at the Olympics-a first for both of us.\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1950, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'The competition in the men's double field was tough, and I have huge respect and congratulations for our competitors.\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 2070, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was a great day for the team overall, with gold, silver, and bronze medals-so proud of our teammates.\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Jordan, you have been an incredible teammate!\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2225, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You have kept me calm and reminded me not to take ourselves too seriously.\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2300, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been so much fun, and I am so proud of what we have accomplished together.\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2380, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'We have had a very special M2x group with Jordan, Ben, Flynn, Jack, and myself over the past two years.\", \"from\": 2382, \"to\": 2486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2425, \"end\": 2431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"score\": 0.9833724236116459, \"rank\": 0.011386886085518117, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\"}, {\"begin\": 2438, \"end\": 2443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Errol_Flynn\", \"score\": 0.999999408649903, \"rank\": 5.913337678436641e-07, \"text\": \"Flynn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Errol_Flynn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Errol_Flynn\"}, {\"begin\": 2445, \"end\": 2449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\", \"score\": 0.9255856296711727, \"rank\": 0.07934302107524534, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have trained incredibly hard yet still tried to enjoy it, building a tight team that pushes and supports each other.\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2606, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ben, you have been a huge part of this journey too-thank you.\", \"from\": 2607, \"to\": 2668, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Thanks to our coach, Gary, and all of the RNZ support team for helping us get here.\", \"from\": 2670, \"to\": 2754, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2713, \"end\": 2716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RNZ\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And a massive thank you for all the support from back home and all over the world.'\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2838, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2840, \"to\": 2888, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2890, \"to\": 2960, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Hugo Hay reveals what George Mills said during row after 5000m Olympic heat  ArrowMORE:Emma Raducanu makes 'downfall' confession ahead of US Open after Olympics snub  ArrowMORE:Cameraman almost causes huge crash by strolling into middle of Olympics track  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2962, \"to\": 3338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3059, \"end\": 3072, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emma Raducanu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 3340, \"to\": 3471, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 3472, \"to\": 3644, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3534, \"end\": 3540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\", \"score\": 0.6784377202962604, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Punchy\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 3646, \"to\": 3777, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy\", \"from\": 3778, \"to\": 3838, \"entities\": []}]}"